This is your new Play 2.0 application
=====================================

This file will be packaged with your application, when using `play dist`.


CURL Commands

Dummy stuff
curl --verbose --header "Content-type: application/json" --request PUT --data '{"name" : "Fabrice"}' http://localhost:9000/rest/testpost


Add products
curl --verbose --header "Content-type: application/json" --request POST --data '{"name" : "Asus TF201", "priceInEuroCents" : "70000"}' http://localhost:9000/products
curl --verbose --header "Content-type: application/json" --request POST --data '{"name" : "Cornflakes", "priceInEuroCents" : "650"}' http://localhost:9000/products
curl --verbose --header "Content-type: application/json" --request POST --data '{"name" : "Renault Scenic", "priceInEuroCents" : "2500000"}' http://localhost:9000/products


Add Customer :
curl --verbose --header "Content-type: application/json" --request POST --data '{"name" : "Fabrice"}' http://localhost:9000/customers
curl --verbose --header "Content-type: application/json" --request POST --data '{"name" : "SÃ©bastien"}' http://localhost:9000/customers

Get Customer details :
curl --verbose --header "Content-type: application/json" --request GET http://localhost:9000/customers/1

Get Product details :
curl --verbose --header "Content-type: application/json" --request GET http://localhost:9000/products/1

